{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_100.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x32,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then I guess I'll listen to your dragon story today..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Whatever you two want is my treat today, so don't hold back. Enjoy yourselves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Then I will."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Are you sure...? I didn't really do anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "You went with him to slay the dragon, right? You have every right to be here and drink for free."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'll have a warm milk please!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Still, I never thought that snot-nosed Juris would grow up to be this big..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I always thought you'd be a pretty good huntsman, but I never thought you'd actually slay the dragon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Although, ever since we were kids, he was always saying that he was gonna slay that dragon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, from that long ago..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, that's right. When I was young, I was told a story about my ancestors who slayed a dragon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x4a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "And that became everything to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Everyone just laughed at him. They told him not to believe that old story."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I can't blame them. It is true that slaying a dragon would bring a huntsman the greatest honor, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That story became a legend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But Juris, don't get carried away, just because you slayed that dragon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Even at your age, you're still a kid."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I didn't plan on getting carried away..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "You never know. You may seem like a calm guy, but you're pretty easy to provoke."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Mix Master, you're being really hard on Juris..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, he has become a stern and boring adult."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "As your \"Big Brother Kyle,\" it's really bumming me out. Isn't that right, Jurry?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xda,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Stop calling me that...<CR>We're not kids anymore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh come on, don't be shy. Isn't it nice to think back to when we were kids?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Huh? You two are childhood friends?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdb,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "It was nothing more than a forced relationship. Our parents knew each other."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I've known him since I was about 13 or 14, and he was about 7."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "He used to just be some cute kid with chubby cheeks."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "He followed me everywhere I went, calling me Big Brother Kyle."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know that!<CR>I wanna hear all about it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Sure. I think it was about a year after we met..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Jurry was aiming to become a huntsman even back then, and one day, he was making beast trap."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "It was a simple pit trap. Jurry started digging a hole in the morning, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "As night came, he still hadn't come home, so the adults went out to look for him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xaa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Then, they heard someone crying from this pit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "\"I dug it too deep, and I can't get<CR>out!\" It was hilarious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xe0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Stop telling all these stories from the past..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Also, one day, when no one took Jurry out to hunt..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xdc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Kyle!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, Jurry's getting mad. Maybe I better not tell this story..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "But I wanna know...<CR>Please continue."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "All right then. So he went out to hunt a rabbit by himself. So thoughtless little Jurry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Decided to try to cook the rabbit over an open flame, but the fire spread to his tent, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Th-Then what happened?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "It turned into a small wildfire. Later on, he was crying because his parents yelled at him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, it's so hard to imagine that, seeing him right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "But that little Jurry grew up to become the huntsman who slayed that dragon..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "As his Big Brother Kyle, I couldn't be happier."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Jeez...childhood friends can be so<CR>wicked..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "(Childhood friends... I wish I had someone like that...)"
        }
    ]
}